    "body": "some updates to blas/lapack usage inside packages to incorporate https://github.com/LLNL/spack/pull/1682 and also fix a few issues.\n\nbuilds on `Ubuntu@16.04`+`gcc@5.4.0`:\n- [x] `dealii@develop ^atlas`\n- [x] `dealii@develop ^openblas`\n- [x] `dealii@develop ^mkl`\n- [x] `cantera ^openblas`\n- [x] `ipopt ^openblas`\n- [x] `Mfem+lapack ^openblas`\n- [x] `SuperluMt ^openblas`\n- [ ] `netliblapack+external-blas ^openblas`\n\np.s. i uninstall system's `blas`/`lapack` to make sure they are not picked up somewhere and lead to a false positive build.\n",
    "performed_via_github_app": null
